write me short poem about love

In a world of chaos, you shine so bright,
Your love is my compass, guiding me right.
Through storms and trials, you're always near,
Your presence, my solace, my heart holds dear.

In your embrace, I find my peace,
A love so pure, it will never cease.
With you by my side, I fear no strife,
For in your love, I've found my life.

So let us dance in this sweet romance,
Bound together in a loving trance.
Forever intertwined, hearts beating as one,
In this eternal love, our journey has begun.
